            ['type' => 'section', 'heading' => 'Leak Detection & Pipe Repair', 'body' => "<p>A hidden leak can quietly cause thousands in water damage before you see a drip. Our plumbers use professional <a href='/plumbing/leak-detection'>leak detection</a> to pinpoint the exact source behind walls, under floors, and in slabs — no demolition guesswork.</p><p>Watch for the warning signs: an unexplained jump in your water bill, running water when everything is off, damp spots or stains, low pressure, or a musty smell that may also call for <a href='/indoor-air-quality/mold-testing'>mold testing</a>.</p><p>From a single corroded section to a full home repipe, we replace aging pipes common in older homes across <a href='/service-areas'>central New Jersey</a> with modern, long-lasting materials.</p>"],
